{"tid":914703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到皇馬個名！高圖爾斯堅忍唔住笑！","createTime":"2018-11-24T13:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T13:23:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70876deb3f5df8fc16f60b4e551e4fba421b679c","tid":914703,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"車路士門將泰拔高圖爾斯為轉會皇家馬德里，近日拒絕歸隊玩失蹤，「藍戰士」已經決定用天價簽阿列沙巴拿加，意味高圖爾斯嘅願望好快可以實現。網上正瘋傳一段影片，據報係球迷喺洛杉磯街頭發現高圖爾斯後拍低，影片中坐喺車內嘅拍攝者，向住高圖爾斯高呼Hala Madrid(皇馬加油)，戴住黑超嘅高圖爾斯就忍唔住流露出燦爛笑容，興奮心情溢於言表。 <br />\n<br />\n據報皇馬好快會用3,500萬鎊轉會費將佢收購，同時會將克羅地亞中場高華錫外借畀車路士。"},{"pid":"015aecc1abda17b1ef1f800d31f6c1e199129860","tid":914703,"uid":138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲笑唔笑得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970d66f82d666710200f937b64d6a067f1baec4b","tid":914703,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"haha madrid<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}